snippet: The all-around champions Simone Biles of the United States and Kohei Uchimura of Japan each added a gold medal in an individual event at the gymnastic world championships.
abstract: American gymnast Simone Biles wins gold medal for women's floor event at world championships and Japan's Kohei Uchimura wins men's parallel bars.
lead_paragraph: The all-around champions Simone Biles of the United States and Kohei Uchimura of Japan each added a gold medal in an individual event at the gymnastic world championships.
